name: ImagDOP Benthic Video Annotations in Condor seamount in 2010
description: Annotations of benthic sessile and mobile speciesrecorded on video by RemoteOperated Vehicle (ROV) during divesperformed in the Condorseamount, located 10 nm SW of FaialIsland, in the Azores archipelago,Portugal. Videos were recorded between180 and 1100 metersdepth.
